   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="Edgeworth_NLS_42180_1841-05-XX_page01.jpg"/>
            <opener>
               <dateline>
                  <placeName ref="./Placeography.xml#1-North-Audley-Street_ENK">1 North Audley Street</placeName><lb/>
                  <date>May 1841</date><lb/>
               </dateline>
               <salute>D.<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Sir</salute></opener><lb/>
            <p>Pray remember that you have<lb/>
               not sent me any answer<lb/>
               about <persName ref="./Personography.xml#MoorG1">Mr. G Moore</persName>'s <unclear>MP</unclear><lb/>
               --<persName ref="./Personography.xml#MoorX1">M.<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi> Moore</persName> will be with me<lb/>
               tomorrow at one o'clock and<lb/>
               what am I to say to her?---<lb/></p>
               <p>I request you will send<lb/>
               me some answer - If you<lb/>
               do not wish to have the <unclear></unclear><lb/>
               send it to me by the Bearer<lb/>
               of this note I entreat that<lb/>
               I may not be obliged to<lb/>
               break my good word which<lb/>
               I have passed for you -</p><lb/>
            <closer>I am D.<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Sir<lb/>
               Yours sincerely<lb/>
               <persName ref="./Personography.xml#EdgeM1">Maria Edgeworth</persName><lb/></closer>
            <postscript><p>Did you not receive a note<lb/>
               from me last week on this subject?<lb/>
               shame! ---<lb/></p></postscript>
         </div>
      </body>
